# pipe_missing.pipe — a pipeline config referencing a missing module (Family C).
#
# The module `A` points at a nonexistent file. The pipe runner must report the
# load/compile failure and exit 2 (the error code), exercising the missing-
# module error-handling path.
#
# Run: ember pipe tests/features/pipe_missing.pipe   (must exit 2)
module A pipe_nonexistent_module.ember
stage A::process
input 1 3
